notesStmt.note: The first copy in the collection is dated 1598, but the collection does not progress in chronological order, ranging back to 1508.

msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: A collection of copies of deeds to territory in Moncelese or Catastico within the Venetian territories, dated from 1508 to 1631 and accompanied by various notarial signatures and signets. Preceded by a table of contents.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in various cursive scripts by several hands.
